<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idefbf9635-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s4803"><num value="4803">§ 4803.</num><heading> Pork and pork product orders</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0" id="idefbf9636-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s4803/a"><num value="a">(a)</num><chapeau> To carry out this chapter, the Secretary shall, in accordance with this chapter, issue and, from time to time, amend orders applicable to persons engaged in—</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idefbf9637-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s4803/a/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> the production and sale of porcine animals, pork, and pork products in the United States; and</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idefbf9638-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s4803/a/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> the importation of porcine animals, pork, or pork products into the United States.</content>
</paragraph>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0" id="idefbf9639-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s4803/b"><num value="b">(b)</num><content> The Secretary may issue such regulations as are necessary to carry out this chapter.</content>
</subsection>
<sourceCredit id="idefbf963a-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/pl/99/198/tXVI/s1614">Pub. L. 99–198, title XVI, § 1614</ref>, <date date="1985-12-23">Dec. 23, 1985</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/99/1609">99 Stat. 1609</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idefbf963b-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="idefbf963c-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="idefbf963d-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section effective <date date="1986-01-01">Jan. 1, 1986</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/99/198/s1631">section 1631 of Pub. L. 99–198</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t7/s4801">section 4801 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
</notes>
